  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a paella pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced aji amarillo pepper and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the flaked sardines, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Deglaze the pan with lemon juice, scraping up any browned bits.",
    "Top the sardine mixture with crushed potato chips.",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes, until the potato chips are crispy.",
    "Serve the Fiery Crunchy Peruvian Sardines Suspiro Limeno hot in the paella pan."
